{
  "stem": "4760.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I bit my teeth.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would not dare giving them the satisfaction, really, to scream.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the more you screamed, the harder they would hit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I-- I screamed somehow, but not really a outburst scream, but I screamed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, I had my 25 slashes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I tell you, I could hardly walk away from that bench.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking they're going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I was thinking of, because, you know, what else can you think about?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I got-- I got those slashes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we went to bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know which way to lay, and which way to sit, and which way to do what.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was in the upper bunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, whoever sleeps down there, I'm going to stay down here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't climb up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was my brother, anyway, so-- so I laid down in the-- in the-- in the-- in the bunk bed and suffered.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what else could you do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the same night, the British-- British Air Force bombed us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they-- they knew about Camp-- Camp Peenemunde.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were bombed all around our camps and all over.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just one bomb came close to our sleeping quarter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how they knew that we were in there, but somebody knew exactly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to-- I have to say, we had some engineers who communicated with England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They made themself little SOS computers, Like you're sending out-- sending out--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Information.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, those things, we knew about our-- amongst our French comrades, you know, the-- the-- that something was going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our-- our conversation was always, I hope we come out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we're going to do as much damage we can do, that they lose the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was all our thinking.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
